               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoners were again indicted on the following Monday for a <rs id="t18781118-43-offence-2" type="offenceDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18781118-43-offence-2" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18781118-43-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>burglary in the dwelling-house of <persName id="t18781118-name-303" type="victimName">
                           <interp inst="t18781118-name-303" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
