                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">ROSS and Amber each</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to previous convictions, Ross in January</hi>, 1876, <hi rend="italic">and Amber in May</hi>, 1871. <hi rend="largeCaps">FOSTER</hi>—<hi rend="italic">
